# This repo deliberately ships CLAUDE.md files (the example vault's conventions
# are part of the product). Un-ignore them in case your global gitignore excludes CLAUDE.md.
!CLAUDE.md

# The skeleton bundles the skills in .claude/skills/ so one copy yields a working
# vault. Un-ignore that path in case your global gitignore excludes .claude/.
!base/skeleton/.claude/
!base/skeleton/.claude/**
